---

### How to Change Fonts:

#### Option A: Use Different Google Fonts

**Step 1:** Visit [Google Fonts](https://fonts.google.com)

**Step 2:** Select fonts you like (e.g., "Montserrat" + "Open Sans")

**Step 3:** Copy the import URL

**Step 4:** Replace Line 1 in [index.css](file:///c:/Users/Purvil/Desktop/Projects/Social%20Agency/Demo-clickboost-media-project/src/index.css):

```css
/* Example: Montserrat + Open Sans */
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');
```

**Step 5:** Update [tailwind.config.ts](file:///c:/Users/Purvil/Desktop/Projects/Social%20Agency/Demo-clickboost-media-project/tailwind.config.ts) (Lines ~20-30):

```typescript
fontFamily: {
  heading: ['Montserrat', 'sans-serif'],  // Changed
  body: ['Open Sans', 'sans-serif'],      // Changed
},
```

