## üé® 2. Changing Colors

All colors are defined in `:root` section (Lines 8-57).

### Main Color Variables:

#### Background Colors (Lines 9-10)
```css
--background: 0 0% 100%;        /* White background */
--foreground: 213 65% 11%;      /* Dark navy text */
```

**Change to light gray background:**
```css
--background: 0 0% 98%;         /* Light gray */
```

---

#### Accent Color (Line 27) - **Most Important!**
```css
--accent: 196 100% 47%;         /* Cyan blue */
```

**Popular Accent Colors:**

| Color | HSL Value | Use Case |
|-------|-----------|----------|
| **Cyan Blue** | `196 100% 47%` | Current ‚úÖ |
| **Electric Blue** | `210 100% 50%` | Tech, Modern |
| **Purple** | `270 70% 50%` | Creative, Luxury |
| **Orange** | `25 95% 53%` | Energetic, Bold |
| **Green** | `142 71% 45%` | Growth, Eco |
| **Pink** | `330 81% 60%` | Creative, Fun |
| **Red** | `0 84% 60%` | Bold, Urgent |

**Example - Change to Purple:**
```css
