## üí° Pro Tips

### Tip 1: Test One Change at a Time
Don't change everything at once - test each change individually

### Tip 2: Use Color Picker
Use browser DevTools color picker to find exact HSL values

### Tip 3: Maintain Contrast
Ensure text is readable on backgrounds (4.5:1 ratio minimum)

### Tip 4: Consistent Accent
Use same accent color throughout for brand consistency

### Tip 5: Save Original
Keep a copy of original values before changing

