## üÜò Troubleshooting

### Colors Not Changing?
- Check if you saved the file (`Ctrl+S`)
- Clear browser cache (`Ctrl+Shift+R`)
- Check for syntax errors (missing semicolons)

### Fonts Not Loading?
- Check Google Fonts URL is correct
- Update [tailwind.config.ts](file:///c:/Users/Purvil/Desktop/Projects/Social%20Agency/Demo-clickboost-media-project/tailwind.config.ts) font family
- Clear browser cache

### Gradients Not Showing?
- Check gradient syntax (commas, parentheses)
- Ensure hex colors are valid (#RRGGBB)
- Try solid color first to debug

